title: CommonAvatarBuilder.BuildDevices
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki


This function (called by [[CommonAvatarBuilder.BuildAvatar]]) mainly sets up the streams and the [[TransformStreamDriver]]s for the devices which the user currently has active. Each of these will have a corresponding BodyNode, an AvatarObjectSlot, and a TransformStreamDriver
